Updated Cypress test run stats for Week 5 & 6 (this week, incomplete)
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ZG_lo2gaupLR_7fNQ6SfNZIKkVtbXmsNXxeCwQ-sdj4/edit?usp=sharing

Caveats:
• Cancelled test runs are excluded from the failure rate, but cancelled test runs may include test failures
• Failure test runs may fail due to real errors (catching real bugs, either caused by frontend change on the PR, or caused by backend changes from previous PRs)
